milestones.description: Vengsarkar and Sandeep Patil's 143-run partnership is IND's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 115 between Gavaskar and Ravi Shastri
Vengsarkar has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 1184 runs, going past Kapil Dev's 1143
Vengsarkar and Sandeep Patil's 143-run partnership is IND's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 134 between Srikkanth and Vengsarkar
